    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cider</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>and<strong> tomato wedges</strong> to the bowl with the dressing and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
