    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are crispy, remove the tray[s] from the oven and carefully slice the shape of a cross through the centre, taking care not to cut all the way through</p><p>Top each potato with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix through with a fork</p>",
