      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>buttered potato</strong> with the <strong>tuna mayo & sweetcorn mix</strong> – this is your <strong>tuna mayo & sweetcorn jacket potato</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>tuna mayo & sweetcorn jacket potato</strong> with the <strong>dressed</strong> <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
